<h2>Dashboard</h2>

<a href="/">
  <button type="button" name="button">Home</button>
  </a>
<h4>Average duration of a ride: <%=@average_ride_duration%></h4>
<h4>Longest ride: <%=@longest_ride%></h4>
<h4>Shortest ride: <%=@shortest_ride%></h4>
<h4>Station with the most rides as a starting place: <%=@station_name_most_rides_start%> (<%=@station_count_most_rides_start%>)</h4>
<h4>Station with the most rides as an ending place: <%=@station_name_most_rides_end%> (<%=@station_count_most_rides_end%>)</h4>
<h4>Most ridden bike with total number of rides for that bike: <%=@bike_most_rides%></h4>
<h4>Least ridden bike with total number of rides for that bike: <%=@bike_least_rides%></h4>
